# ============================================================
# AI Office Assistant - .gitignore
# 原則：追蹤「框架」，忽略「資料與機密」
# ============================================================

# === 機密 ===
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
MASTER_API_KEY.txt
.mcp.json

# === 資料庫 ===
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db.bak*
*.db-journal
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

# === 大型 / 二進位資料檔 ===
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.csv
*.pdf
*.pptx
*.docx

# === 專案資料（只追蹤 _template）===
projects/*/
!projects/_template/

# === 共用知識庫（公司專屬知識）===
shared/kb/decisions.md
shared/kb/active_rules_summary.md
shared/kb/_index.md
shared/kb/architecture_overview.md
shared/kb/error_patterns.md
shared/kb/evolution_log.md
shared/kb/tool_registry.md
shared/kb/file_registry.json
shared/kb/*.md
shared/kb/dynamic/
shared/kb/external/
shared/kb/memory/
shared/kb/knowledge_graph/
shared/kb/ops_log/

# === Skills 內容（公司專屬領域知識）===
# 忽略所有 skill 子目錄內容
.claude/skills/*/
# 但保留 _skill_template 範本
!.claude/skills/_skill_template/
!.claude/skills/.gitkeep

# === Skills-on-demand 內容 ===
.claude/skills-on-demand/*/
!.claude/skills-on-demand/.gitkeep

# === Claude Code 個人設定 ===
.claude/agent-memory/
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/CLAUDE.v2.7.backup.md

# === Python artifacts ===
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
*.egg

# === Conda / venv ===
.conda/
.venv/
venv/
env/
requirements-lock.txt

# === IDE ===
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# === OS ===
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# === Playwright MCP cache ===
.playwright-mcp/

# === Backup / Temp ===
*.backup
*.bak
*.tmp
*.temp

# === 根目錄散落檔案 ===
parse_db_pa004.py
